passages.name: Untitled Passage
passages.text:
Hi! I have a thing that I want to get fixed!
[[Sure! What is it?]]
[[Tough beans! Please leave!]]
passages.cleanText: Hi! I have a thing that I want to get fixed!

passages.name: Sure! What is it?
passages.text:
It's this family heirloom, it broke down after I completely submerged it in water, I have no idea why
[[Do you think it could maybe be the water?]]

links.linkText: Do you think it could maybe be the water?

passages.cleanText: It's this family heirloom, it broke down after I completely submerged it in water, I have no idea why

passages.name: Do you think it could maybe be the water?
passages.text: Wow, now that you say it, maybe electonical devices can't deal with that much saltwater? I'll stop bringing it to the beach then!
